Yeah, a couple times, but haven't for a while. They're usually pretty competitive. Tim and I got dropped off the back a few times, but I also was able to stay with them a couple times. I think depending on who is there determines how fast they go. They meet in the parking lot around building 4 at 11:25ish and depart at 11:30. If they do the standard loop they return around 12:45, again depending on their pace. Sometimes they'll climb old la honda up to skyline, then go down skyline to 84, descend that and continue on the standard loop. that ads almost an extra 45 minutes. You can take shorter routes too, to get back sooner. When Tim and I used to go we would take a shorter route cause we couldn't take as long of a lunch.
